title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 13 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 13 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: Covid vaccine mandates are spreading all over the country. Philadelphia, New Orleans, San Francisco, L.A., New York City, when will it stop? Stanford University demands students get vaccine and a weekly covid test. Biden is discussing mandating vaccines for interstate travel, but the border is wide open. Biden administration tries to spin the unmitigated disaster in Afghanistan.
